Update BIOS

Set BIOS
  UEFI = On
  Legacy Mode = Off
  Secure Boot = Off
  Optional
    Port security = Off (for docking)
    Thunderbolt = On
    Intel XXX = On

Install Ubuntu 16.04 LTS

Trim launcher

Remove softwares

Get softwares
  Update softwares with Software Updater
  Get from Software Center
    GParted
  Get from developer website
    Chrome
    Atom
  Get with command line
    $ sudo apt install screen tree exfat-utils exfat-fuse git

Set System Settings
  Auto-hide launcher
  Add show desktop icon to the launcher
  Decrease typing delay (t)
  Increase typing speed (maximum)
  Enable natural scrolling
  Show weekday
  Show date and month
  Use 24-hour time
  Show seconds

Set vi as the default text editor
  $ sudo update-alternatives --config editor

Optional

  Set File view (Edit --> Preferences)

  Enable SSH
    $ sudo apt-get install openssh-server
    $ sudo service ssh status

  Configure SSH
    $ sudo vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
    $ sudo service ssh restart
